# CVE-2026-27904 — glob backtracking (minimatch/node internals)
# ReDoS vulnerability in glob pattern matching within npm tooling.
# Our app does not expose user-controlled input to glob pattern evaluation.
CVE-2026-27904  # glob ReDoS in npm internals, no user input reaches glob | reviewed: 2026-06-10 | next review: 2026-09-10
